fr.cnrs.iees.properties

Interface SimpleWriteProtectablePropertyList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.DataContainer, PropertyListGetters, PropertyListSetters, ReadOnlyPropertyList, SimplePropertyList, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.WriteProtectable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SharedWriteProtectablePropertyListImpl

    public interface SimpleWriteProtectablePropertyList
extends SimplePropertyList, fr.ens.biologie.generic.WriteProtectable

    A property list for graph GraphElements that can be made read-only on demand.

    1. Immutable, i.e. the list of properties does not change after construction.
    2. Default properties: none.
    Author:
    Jacques Gignoux - 29-8-2017
